cs.RO, cs.SE, cs.EM, cs.SY, cs.PL 

The paper focuses on using robotic platforms as a basis for research in self-driving cars and collaborative vehicle fleets, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the process of configuring hardware/software interfaces, which is a software engineering (cs.SE) task. Additionally, the paper deals with cyber-physical systems (cs.EM) and system engineering (cs.SY) in the context of robotic platforms. Finally, the paper applies model checking using declarative languages, which is a topic in programming languages (cs.PL).
